===Etymology===
Coined in 1813 by [[w:Thomas Young (scientist)|Sir Thomas Young]], from {{prefix|Indo|European|lang=en}}, relating to the geographical extremes in [[India]] and [[Europe]] (which was valid before the discovery of [[Tocharian]] languages in the early 20th century).

